      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAHLAWAN (8) showed good speed to lead over 1400m at this track last start but faded right out of it to finish sixth. Rates highly on best form and he looks set to run well with a bit less pressure over this longer trip. ENTICING (1) last appeared seven weeks ago over 1600m at this track when he finished third. This is his first run for the S Dunderdale stable. In the mix despite the gap between runs. VARIANT (10) was in the firing line on the turn and progressed nicely last start to finish a close second over 1600m at this track after missing the placings at the previous appearance. Finds a tougher race but a win is not out of the question. STORM DEITY (11) turned in a much better effort last time out to score by half a length over 1700m at this track. Has his share of ability. Hard to beat again.",
